<p><strong>Bug Report</strong>: Vending Machine is deleting concept of value of individual dollars</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>Issue</strong>: A vending machine on Earth is removing concept of value from money inserted into it.</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>Location</strong>: Brooklyn, New York, United States of America, Earth, Sol System, Milky Way Galaxy, Universe #727</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>Expected Result</strong>: Machine accepts money, and then ejects it if it does not register as money.</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>Actual Result</strong>: Machine accepts money, removes the concept of value from money, and then ejects a piece of paper.</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>Steps to Reproduce</strong>: Create a vending machine with the current code for the vending machine at the specified location.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none">
<div class="code">
<p>if (dollar.value = null || dollar.wrinkled)<br />
{<br />
return dollar;<br />
}<br />
else<br />
{<br />
currentvalue += dollar.value;<br />
return null;<br />
}</p>
</div>
